<h1>砍</h1><p class=neha><span style="color:#009900;">kǎn</span><span class=alesi>(kan3)</span> <span class=lesi>// pronunciation of 砍 in Mandarin Pinyin</span></p><h2>Basic information about 砍</h2><div class=abo>
<p><b>Unihan definition:</b> <a href="/dictionary/hack" style="color:black;">hack</a>, <a href="/dictionary/chop" style="color:black;">chop</a>, <a href="/dictionary/cut" style="color:black;">cut</a>, fell</p><p><b>Number of strokes:</b> 9<br><small>Examples of other characters consisting of 9 strokes: <a href="/character/是" title="shi4: indeed, yes, right; to be; demonstrative pronoun, this, that">是</a>, <a href="/character/说" title="shuo1: speak, say, talk; scold, upbraid">说</a>, <a href="/character/要" title="yao4: necessary, essential; necessity">要</a>, <a href="/character/种" title="zhong3: seed; race, breed; to plant">种</a>, <a href="/character/面" title="mian4: face; surface; plane; side, dimension">面</a>, <a href="/character/看" title="kan4: look, see; examine, scrutinize">看</a>, <a href="/character/前" title="qian2: in front, forward; preceding">前</a>, <a href="/character/点" title="dian3: dot, speck, spot; point, degree">点</a>, <a href="/character/将" title="jiang1: will, going to, future; general">将</a>, <a href="/character/很" title="hen3: very, quite, much">很</a></small></p><p><b>Radical:</b> <a href="/character/石" title="Kangxi radical 112">石</a>&nbsp;112.4</p><p><b>HSK level:</b> 5 <br><small>Other HSK 5 characters: <a href="/character/晕" title="yun1: halo in sky; fog; dizzy, faint">晕</a>, <a href="/character/抄" title="chao1: copy, confiscate, seize">抄</a>, <a href="/character/狮" title="shi1: lion">狮</a>, <a href="/character/剪" title="jian3: scissors; cut, divide, separate">剪</a>, <a href="/character/叉" title="cha1: crotch; fork, prong">叉</a>, <a href="/character/拐" title="guai3: kidnap, abduct; turn">拐</a>, <a href="/character/寓" title="yu4: residence; lodge; dwell">寓</a>, <a href="/character/捐" title="juan1: contribute; give up, renounce">捐</a>, <a href="/character/歪" title="wai1: slant; inclined; askewd, awry">歪</a>, <a href="/character/粘" title="zhan1: viscous, mucous; glutinous">粘</a> <a href="/character-list/hsk/level-5" title="List of HSK 5 characters"